you used to be a cop, Father.

102
00:05:23,889 --> 00:05:26,530
- I'll ask around too.
- Yes.

103
00:05:26,530 --> 00:05:29,530
All right. Goodness, anyway...

104
00:05:30,100 --> 00:05:32,300
I really hope
this doesn't wear your mom down.

105
00:05:32,300 --> 00:05:34,739
Dad, focus.

106
00:05:34,739 --> 00:05:35,939
Just focus on finding Grandma.

107
00:05:35,939 --> 00:05:37,610
I'll take care of Mom, all right?

108
00:05:40,679 --> 00:05:41,679
Oh, dear.

109
00:05:51,749 --> 00:05:53,619
Mom,

110
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:56,290
shall we watch a movie together
at the terminal?

111
00:05:56,619 --> 00:05:57,960
Just the two of us. What do you say?

112
00:05:57,960 --> 00:06:00,389
Let's watch a movie together
and eat popcorn too, okay?

113
00:06:00,389 --> 00:06:01,460
Let's do that.

114
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,600
Mom.

115
00:06:21,879 --> 00:06:23,119
Myung Ja.

116
00:06:23,619 --> 00:06:26,119
Don't be like this.
Let's go home, okay?

117
00:06:26,420 --> 00:06:28,020
You need to get some sleep.

118
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,420
That day...

119
00:06:31,629 --> 00:06:33,800
