- No, how could I have slept well?
- I'm a cool tomato

209
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:29,319
Tomato

210
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:32,449
No Ah, we did so well.
We're the best.

211
00:12:32,449 --> 00:12:33,449
Tomato

212
00:12:35,859 --> 00:12:38,429
- Looking buff and cool
- Should we call the police on her?

213
00:12:39,559 --> 00:12:43,599
So, did you get any updates
from Kkotsan Police?

214
00:12:43,599 --> 00:12:44,599
No.

215
00:12:45,469 --> 00:12:47,839
Oh, boy. Let's go to Ilsan...

216
00:12:48,439 --> 00:12:49,939
and Paju today.

217
00:12:49,939 --> 00:12:50,939
Okay, Gyeong Tae.

218
00:12:53,839 --> 00:12:55,839
Oh, Myung Ja. How have you been?

219
00:12:56,740 --> 00:12:57,750
Hi.

220
00:12:58,809 --> 00:13:01,420
What brings you here
so early in the morning?

221
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:04,849
You should just stay at home.

222
00:13:04,849 --> 00:13:07,219
I'll look around
with Detective An today.

223
00:13:07,719 --> 00:13:09,359
Don't worry about Mother.

224
00:13:09,359 --> 00:13:10,760
