244
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:10,020
but she refuses to listen to me.

245
00:14:10,020 --> 00:14:12,689
She seemed really upset.

246
00:14:13,219 --> 00:14:16,189
Gyeong Tae was just trying
to do his best too.

247
00:14:16,189 --> 00:14:20,189
Goodness, if you don't know
the struggles she has been through,

248
00:14:20,189 --> 00:14:22,229
you should just keep your mouth shut
and stay out of it.

249
00:14:23,229 --> 00:14:25,900
Throughout their entire marriage,

250
00:14:25,900 --> 00:14:27,329
